{"tid":2259301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平趁美國內鬥，喺中共五中全會確立「總書記獨裁制」，權力同地位直逼毛澤東時代嘅黨主席，正式成為「無冕皇帝」","createTime":"2020-10-26T17:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T04:27:56.000Z","uid":155095,"like":80,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"ac922a28edff2013bab02a6ed6c0ee2601cf20f5","tid":2259301,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:00:37.000Z","msg":"source: <del>星島日報</del><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">加埋美國民主黨同拜登助陣<br />\n<br />\n習近平今次真正成為習皇帝</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/10/GettyImages-489974606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FGettyImages-489974606.jpg&h=1e3c44ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[<del>星島日報報道</del>] <ins>五中全會</ins>還將通過《<strong>中國共產黨中央委員會工作條例</strong>》。在《決策部署》一章規定，中央政治局會議、中央政治局常委會會議、中央書記處辦公會議，<span class=\"red\">議題均由<strong>中共總書記</strong>確定，中央決策議事協調機構會議議題由<strong>總書記</strong>確定或審定</span>。分析認為，《工作條例》有助鞏固習近平的領袖地位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/cBcl0RasTYo/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FcBcl0RasTYo%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=358c6290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「條例」共八章三十五條，就加強中共中央委員會工作，對中共中央的領導地位、領導體制、領導職權、領導方式、決策部署、自身建設等作出全面規定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/8b287728-0d31-11ea-8a33-005056bfe576/w:1280/p:4x3/%20%E8%A2%AB%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E4%B9%A0%E7%9A%87%E5%B8%9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F8b287728-0d31-11ea-8a33-005056bfe576%2Fw%3A1280%2Fp%3A4x3%2F%2520%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25A7%25B0%25E4%25B8%25BA%25E4%25B9%25A0%25E7%259A%2587%25E5%25B8%259D.jpg&h=84db4545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共中央發出通知指出，制定「條例」是中共黨和國家政治生活的一件大事，堅持和加強黨的全面領導，最重要的是堅定維護「<span class=\"red\">以<strong>習近平</strong>同志為<strong>核心</strong>的黨中央權威和集中統一領導</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200717/1536pix/1594987018_bbd6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200717%2F1536pix%2F1594987018_bbd6.png&h=954a4c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據「條例」，<span class=\"red\">總書記將正式取得決策過程中的議題設定權</span>，而不僅止於《黨章》第二十三條所授予的兩項正式職權&mdash;召集政治局、政治局常委會會議，並主持中央書記處的工作而已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/26170801/adsfgsdgageweg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F26170801%2Fadsfgsdgageweg.png&h=d8965e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條例又特別提到，中央委員及政治局委員亦必須將<span class=\"red\">維護<strong>習近平</strong>的全黨<strong>核心</strong>地位</span>以及維護黨中央權威和集中統一領導作為根本政治要求，確保黨中央政令暢通、令行禁止，確保黨中央決策部署落地見效。政治學者陳道銀分析，條例是把習近平執政以來，特別是十九大以來的黨內一些做法制度化，將黨章的原則條例化。"},{"pid":"04b224abceeff296d7d4638f82b4810640755a6c","tid":2259301,"uid":343361,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c868bd18ed9a79f665cb32067002ed0893ef0c20","tid":2259301,"uid":258345,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:04:37.000Z","msg":"香港男人唔係大男人既，係想伴侶以佢為核心作出生活上所有決定姐"},{"pid":"8cfe1c78fe96a1ca4683ea93247f6c654bf4a5f7","tid":2259301,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:07:26.000Z","msg":"終身執政官,咁下一步係唔係稱帝?"},{"pid":"c55c9cd4a4bed33cc2d985bcbd1579d1f03d9106","tid":2259301,"uid":59461,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:11:10.000Z","msg":"係件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0ef33c982e73ae31c7f93b28219f5086dfe978","tid":2259301,"uid":152705,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"04b224abceeff296d7d4638f82b4810640755a6c","tid":2259301,"uid":343361,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"賭緊身家, 敗登win嘅話開埋turbo都得"},{"pid":"92563e4d9ddfc5f632c1423b5eea406e1604d9ad","tid":2259301,"uid":343361,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bb8f09e7d7391ee9a18b51e6631d456d33a38b1","tid":2259301,"uid":296361,"like":71,"dislike":2,"score":69,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"當年毛澤東都係用威望同政治手段壓服所有人。都冇白紙黑字寫晒出黎咁誇張。我絕對同意，唔好仲講大陸有咩派咩派啦，係大陸國內已經完全冇晒權力制衡。<br />\n<br />\ne家牌已經揭晒出黎，點解維利會咁強硬，做咁多我哋覺得不智既事，係因為內部，佢已經100%完全掌控，而外部，佢哋連美國既傳統精英，傳媒，同政治領導層，都全部買起晒，如果唔係中間出個異類侵出嚟，根本選紅選藍，都唔會有分別。"},{"pid":"66450c296f1adcd33aee495093ab9c7dc14bc08e","tid":2259301,"uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:33:39.000Z","msg":"內文寫得好奇怪？<br />\n<br />\n唔明改左啲乜"},{"pid":"4209ab27abf599ace2b5ee8de87f30078c25c259","tid":2259301,"uid":195136,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:37:07.000Z","msg":"所謂民族復興原來係恢復帝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好快變第二個北韓，到時你想走都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32d478217a4a28d59795bfa6a63a00d4243060f","tid":2259301,"uid":195136,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"92563e4d9ddfc5f632c1423b5eea406e1604d9ad","tid":2259301,"uid":343361,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"0e0ef33c982e73ae31c7f93b28219f5086dfe978","tid":2259301,"uid":152705,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"04b224abceeff296d7d4638f82b4810640755a6c","tid":2259301,"uid":343361,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"賭緊身家, 敗登win嘅話開埋turbo都得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:37:56.000Z","msg":"習大大有解放軍<br />\n李克強有咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd4cf6cfb51e43ac4db9d234f4a82c2a6efdcc7","tid":2259301,"uid":343361,"li